      "comment": "MY MATE ROBBIE (7) comes here after a handy win at this track over 305m in 17.61. Smart win latest and looks a key chance again here. COSTLY HABITS (1) was strongly fancied last time but finished second (18.02), beaten half a length. Has good speed and is aided by the cherry draw. Expected to be in this for a long way. MISS PEACHY (8) had the drop on the lead from the rails draw last start but could only manage third, beaten 2.5 lengths (18.18) at this track in a Maiden over 305m. Must be included in calculations. OPAL LIMES (2) is a course and distance winner who is right in the equation.",
